{
  "texts": [
    "This synthesis is crucial for generating responses that are not only accurate and relevant but also contextually coherent and linguistically fluid.",
    "Additionally, the selection of external knowledge bases poses its own set of challenges.",
    "The criteria for selection must balance the breadth and depth of coverage with considerations of access speed, update frequency, and compatibility with the model's architecture.",
    "The reliance on external sources also introduces potential issues of bias and variance in the information quality, which can affect the model's outputs.",
    "Finally, this research underscores the importance of continuous learning and adaptation mechanisms within LLMs to accommodate the integration of external knowledge."
  ]
}